#

Stuffed Bell Peppers with Ground Turkey and Brown Rice

45 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Low CarbHigh Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseLunch

Tags:

EasyHealthyOne-PotComfort Food

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with savory ground turkey and wholesome brown rice, baked to perfection.

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4 large
  • ground turkey: 1 pound
  • cooked brown rice: 1 cup
  • onion: 1 medium, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • shredded cheese: 1 cup (optional)
